the Regional Forum of Investors for Southern Africa, the official
Mozambican News Agency reported.
</P>
<P>
The Mozambican president said that the intervention of Senegal
and Guinea has been supported by the Organization of the African
Unity (OAU) which passed the resolutions in favor of the
