including Armymen are involved in the fight against rising water
in central Hunan Province.
</P>
<P>
The central and northern parts of the province were battered by
heavy rain from June 12 to 16 that destroyed crops, washed away
houses, and damaged infrastructure in 10 cities and counties.
</P>
<P>
Five people were killed and one was reported missing in a
landslide that was caused by the torrential rains.
</P>
<P>
