Zhicheng-Liuzhou Railway line had been repaired and was open to
traffic, after having been closed for about 17 hours.
</P>
<P>
As the water level in the province's major rivers continued to
approach the danger line, local people and armymen were
reinforcing dykes and dams to get ready for more rains that are
expected in a couple of days.
 
