<TEXT>
<P>
LA-TOUR-DU-PIN, France, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Fautino Asprilla has
been kicked out of Colombian squad, head coach hernan Dario Gomez said
here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Asprilla's exclusion from the rest of competition followed comments
made by the Parma striker on Colombian radio which questioned the
tactics used by Gomez and the performance of whole team in their 1-0
loss to Romania.
</P>
<P>
"He broke the rules by speaking that way to a journalist. He knew
what he was doing, he has excluded himself," said Gomez after
Wednesday morning's training session here.
</P>
<P>
