staff to visit China since Kazakhstan got its independence, and
that his visit will help bilateral military relations and friendly
cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Fu discussed China's views on the Asia-Pacific and global
situation and China's foreign policy, national defence, and
military development with Gen. Ertaev.
</P>
<P>
Ertaev expressed his satisfaction with relations
between Kazakhstan and China and between their armed forces and
said he hopes his visit will help increase cooperation.
</P>
<P>
He also praised China's achievements in developing its military
and said that the Kazakh army is willing to learn from China in
this.
</P>
