million ringgit (68.434 million dollars) from Tuesday's 127.587
million shares worth 284.106 million ringgit (70.149 million
dollars).
</P>
<P>
On the second board, turnover, however, increased to 8.659
million shares worth 13.277 million ringgit (3.278 million
dollars) from 6.233 million shares valued at 8.521 million ringgit
(2.103 million dollars) on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Off-market deals jumped to 73.693 million shares valued at
60.68 million ringgit (14.982 million dollars) from 4.23 million
shares worth 13.449 million ringgit (3.32 million dollars) on
Tuesday.
