<HEADLINE> Bangladesh Finalizes Draft Industrial Policy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, June 17 (Xinhua) -- Bangladesh's draft industrial policy
1998 was finalized Tuesday with the objective of achieving
self-reliance through rapid industrialization, said a press
release of the Industrial Policy Formation Committee reaching here
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
