Sargsian defeated Mantilla 6-3, 6-7 (5-7), 7-6 (7-3), Black
eliminated the Australian 7-6 (7-2), 7-6 (7-3) while Prinosil beat
Arazi 6-3, 6-4.
</P>
<P>
Fourth seed Cedric Pioline of France, last year's beaten
Wimbledon finalist, upset Thomas Nydahl of Sweden 6-4, 6-4 in a
rain-delayed match. 
